{"tid":2163022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官轟控方擴暴動範圍  不滿變警總「一帶」：我要準確不要彈性","createTime":"2020-08-18T12:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T12:10:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1da2c1ce09ab789a6ce095c13d317096d4836bd9","tid":2163022,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/ZO63N74L7RGI5PCF33XZHD3SIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FZO63N74L7RGI5PCF33XZHD3SIA%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5pUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=fef34e30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FZO63N74L7RGI5PCF33XZHD3SIA%2F&h=32555ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/ZO63N74L7RGI5PCF33XZHD3SIA/</a><br />\n<br />\n官轟控方擴暴動範圍 <br />\n不滿變警總「一帶」：我要準確不要彈性<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年6月26日大批反送中示威者包圍警察總部，當日有便衣警員聲稱欲往警總上班時，遭多名示威者追打，一度手持水刮與示威者對峙，最終由同袍打開警總捲閘救走。有地盤工被指有份毆打該便衣警，被控襲擊傷人及暴動等罪，案件昨在區院開審。控方開案前申請修改暴動範圍，稱要令控罪有更大彈性，惟法官郭啟安斥責「我要準確性呀，彈性就係不確定性」，指被告無「Ｘ光眼」不會知其他地方發生何事，不應為其他非法行為負責，控方最終撤回修訂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5EoUDfjTLdCRmyLIMIpP4yUMH6s=/902x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6KBGGSFJ25BOTC46EXAPMC5QJI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5EoUDfjTLdCRmyLIMIpP4yUMH6s%3D%2F902x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6KBGGSFJ25BOTC46EXAPMC5QJI.jpg&h=c60be7e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法官郭啟安<br />\n<br />\n已還柙八個月的25歲被告。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8xFjkF3rLF7c7Vf-lGMGk4jZ2Wg=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EFXWBITQI5FBFD577LZ5USO7G4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8xFjkF3rLF7c7Vf-lGMGk4jZ2Wg%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEFXWBITQI5FBFD577LZ5USO7G4.jpg&h=04766162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉案警員張金福案發當晚在警總取水刮及雪糕筒保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方終撤回收訂<br />\n<br />\n控方大律師吳美華甫開庭，即申請修訂暴動罪的控罪詳情，欲將「警察總部外」改為「警察總部一帶」。法官郭啟安問原因及是否有證據支持，吳稱修改可使控罪範圍更闊，附近有性質相近暴動，遭郭官狠批。郭官指被告身處軍器廠街，如何跟另一地方的其他人集結，明言「你講唔出我唔會畀你改」。主控指被告未參與前，附近集結已演變成暴動，有人「掟嘢、拉住事主唔畀佢走、辱罵等」。郭官重申，被告「冇可能參與佢唔知悉嘅事」，之前曾審理「赴湯杜火」暴動一案的他並說：「如果你唔明嘅話，可以睇返我（上一宗案）份判詞。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FW5AriARrOr9OHsQkLe7GWOsWdg=/945x1871/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VMVCLNF4FZCCZKHUV3U3TANURY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFW5AriARrOr9OHsQkLe7GWOsWdg%3D%2F945x1871%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVMVCLNF4FZCCZKHUV3U3TANURY.gif&h=6309fe89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳索取律政司意見後撤回申請，但拒絕接納被告承認非法集結罪，不接受辯方稱被告只在警總正門外非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞指，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而涉案警員張金福當。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方翌晨拆下包住警總閉路電視其中一個垃圾膠袋時，膠紙留有被告拇指指紋。案情又指張金福因被打臉，其口腔潰瘍因而破裂，他今早將出庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC825/1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9"}]}